  "texts": [
    "There are also geographical and population gaps in developing countries like Ethiopia where no sufficient investigation has been undertaken about employee engagement level and effects on organizational performance [36].",
    "Almost all empirical evidences about employee engagement and effects from western and from industry developed countries.",
    "In Ethiopia, even though different scholars attempted to study about employee engagement and effects on organizational performance [13,16,17,30,52].",
    "Rate of engaged employees have not been yet explored and identified.",
    "But there is only study conducted by Yallew [57] on higher education in Ethiopia recent development and challenges."
  ]
